  <body>
    <%- include('./partials/_header.ejs') %> <%-
    include('./partials/_navigation.ejs') %>
    <section class="container">
      <div>
        <p>
          At Pets-R-Us your pet is in the best hands all day and all night. You
          dog will love playing with other dogs in our state of the art
          facility. It has 5 playrooms that your dog can venture into. Each room
          has furniture for your dog to play on. While your dog is playing all
          day it will come time to get some rest. Our sleeping area for yur pet
          is top notch. We have cushion flooring so your dog is comfortable
          while staying in the sleeping pen. Our staff love your pets and are
          trained to give your pet the best experience.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h1>Pricing</h1>
        <table>
          <tr>
            <th>Number of dogs</th>
            <th>Nights</th>
            <th>Price</th>
